---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Us" 
  description="Learn about Exotic Pet Atlas - your trusted source for comprehensive exotic pet care information, veterinary resources, and legal guidance since 2024."
  keywords="about exotic pet atlas, exotic pet experts, pet care authority, mission, team"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">About Exotic Pet Atlas</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Exotic Pet Atlas was founded in 2024 with a clear mission: to provide accurate, comprehensive, and accessible information about exotic pet ownership in the United States. We believe that responsible pet ownership starts with education, and we're committed to being the most trusted resource for exotic pet enthusiasts, potential owners, and current caregivers.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Our platform combines expert veterinary knowledge, up-to-date legal information, and practical care guidance to help you make informed decisions about exotic pet ownership.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Expertise</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-pastel-blue mb-2">üî¨ Veterinary Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We work closely with board-certified exotic animal veterinarians and specialists certified by the American Board of Veterinary Practitioners (ABVP). Our care guides are reviewed by professionals with extensive experience in exotic pet medicine.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-pastel-blue mb-2">‚öñÔ∏è Legal Research</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Our legal information is sourced directly from state statutes, wildlife agency regulations, and official government publications. We update our database regularly to reflect the latest legislative changes affecting exotic pet ownership.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-pastel-blue mb-2">üìö Evidence-Based Care</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            All care recommendations are based on peer-reviewed veterinary literature, established husbandry standards, and input from experienced exotic pet keepers and breeders with decades of combined experience.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">What We Cover</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-pastel-green pl-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Pet Care Guides</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Comprehensive species-specific care information including habitat, diet, health, and behavior</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-pastel-pink pl-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">State Laws & Regulations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Up-to-date legal status, permit requirements, and banned species by state</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-pastel-blue pl-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Exotic Veterinarians</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Directory of specialized vets, certifications, and emergency contacts</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-pastel-purple pl-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Setup Guides</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Detailed habitat requirements, equipment recommendations, and budget options</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Commitment to Accuracy</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-pastel-green mr-2 mt-1">‚úì</span>
          <span><strong>Regular Updates:</strong> We review and update all content quarterly, with legal information updated monthly</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-pastel-green mr-2 mt-1">‚úì</span>
          <span><strong>Source Citations:</strong> Every factual claim is backed by official sources, veterinary research, or expert consultation</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-pastel-green mr-2 mt-1">‚úì</span>
          <span><strong>Transparency:</strong> We clearly distinguish between legal requirements, professional recommendations, and community best practices</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-pastel-green mr-2 mt-1">‚úì</span>
          <span><strong>User Safety:</strong> We prioritize animal welfare and owner safety in all recommendations</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-pastel-beige rounded-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Have questions, suggestions, or corrections? We welcome feedback from veterinarians, experienced keepers, and the exotic pet community.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="inline-block bg-pastel-green text-gray-800 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-80 transition">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8 text-center">
      Last updated: January 2026
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
